snippet.title: Elon Musk Defended Johnny Depp & Spoke Against Amber Heard?
snippet.description:
Elon Musk Defended Johnny Depp & Spoke Against Amber Heard?

Amber Heard and Johnny Depp are no more together since they got divorced in 2017, whereas the ex-couple still see each other, but in lawsuits. While Heard accused Depp of the Domestic Violence case, the Hollywood actor decided not to stay numb and speak up against the wrong claims. Well, we all know how happy the couple was back in 2011 when they met on the sets shooting for a movie together.

The romantic relationship and the bond between the lovely couple started to grow as they announced their relationship a year later. Moreover, things were going quite smoothly and interesting for them until the couple decided to visit Honolulu for a vacation. The tables did turn and since then, the ex-husband's wife is not on a good note.
